{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"efa4ec4b55","title":"给周世钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"102deb2df1","index":0,"year":1951,"month":3,"day":19,"articleId":"efa4ec4b55"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"581befd93b","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，字停元，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学，当时任湖南省立第一师范学校校长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f3a60597f0","type":"title","text":"给周世印的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"581befd93b","type":"paragraph","text":"停元兄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"8c8e5d5003","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十四日给我的信收到了，谢谢您。一月二十九日的信及学生们的签名信也收到了。你的三项计划很好。进研究院很有意义，可以安心读几个月书。读完去东北华东考察一次也极好。第三项计划可能有些困难，如在两三年后实施也有可能办到","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"de2334d914","type":"paragraph","text":"我在乡下住，没有病，专为休养，暂不进城。容后面叙。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"748cc35420","type":"paragraph","text":"祝安好！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"eb15aaff2a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"},{"id":"ec2d138fcb","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十九日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55"}],"page":{"id":"b0ab13b78e","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"efa4ec4b55","start":170,"end":170}}}},"__N_SSG":true}